{"_id":"INwWyZnSgvP4HTmm","name":"Boots with hidden pockets. I am the greatest criminal mastermind of all time, and the echoes of my misdeeds have reverberated around the world. Thanks to my incredible cunning, I have always made fools of the authorities, pulled off the most incredible thefts, and manipulated institutions like puppets in my hands. All this until I crossed paths with the World’s Most Famous Investigator. I knew immediately that he would be a challenge worthy of my talents, and for years we battled each other through misdeeds and investigations. On the day of our showdown, however, I realized the truth that I had always tried to hide in my heart. What united us was not rivalry, but the love that can only be felt for someone who is your perfect better half. Feigning death, we retired to private life, but the idyll was shortlived. Called to duty on an international case, he broke our pact and returned to the limelight to do what he does best. Distraught and wounded, I took refuge in the Order. As a Hunter, I used my brilliant mind to fight the darkness and forget my lost love. Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment8.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","ownerKey":"cazador.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","role":"equipment","sequence":8}},"system":{"description":"Boots with hidden pockets. I am the greatest criminal mastermind of all time, and the echoes of my misdeeds have reverberated around the world. Thanks to my incredible cunning, I have always made fools of the authorities, pulled off the most incredible thefts, and manipulated institutions like puppets in my hands. All this until I crossed paths with the World’s Most Famous Investigator. I knew immediately that he would be a challenge worthy of my talents, and for years we battled each other through misdeeds and investigations. On the day of our showdown, however, I realized the truth that I had always tried to hide in my heart. What united us was not rivalry, but the love that can only be felt for someone who is your perfect better half. Feigning death, we retired to private life, but the idyll was shortlived. Called to duty on an international case, he broke our pact and returned to the limelight to do what he does best. Distraught and wounded, I took refuge in the Order. As a Hunter, I used my brilliant mind to fight the darkness and forget my lost love. Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment8.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
